\f3 \'92\'86\'93\'f1\'95\'61
\f0 ) is a colloquial term typically used to describe early teens who have delusions of grandeur, who so desperately want to stand out that they have convinced themselves they have hidden knowledge or secret powers. The term has been popularized by the light novel and anime series Love, Chunibyo & Other Delusions.[1][2][3][4] The term translates literally to "middle two disease", i.e. middle-school second-year syndrome.\
